title: Hellboy BPRD - Complete Series (Ocnosis)
description:
Hi guys its been awhile,

here is my Hellboy and BPRD collection in my reading order

there are a couple of minor changes here and there from what other torrents of the same type offer, for example Hellboy the Island now has the epilogue attached to it.

You will also find more of the original comics, such as black and white Dark Horse Presents as well as the Color versions from the Trades

also i chose to release this torrent now because a few series just wrapped up or went on a long pause and the upcoming ones will only be completed in a very long while

thanks to all the original scanners, ENJOY!


Ocnosis



(oh and buy them if you like them, i suggest the library editions)


*** Reading Order Edit -> BPRD War on Frogs issue #3 should be read AFTER reading BPRD the Black Flame
